<title identifier="/us/usc/t1"><num value="1">Title 1—</num><heading>GENERAL PROVISIONS</heading>
<chapter identifier="/us/usc/t1/ch1"><num value="1">CHAPTER 1—</num><heading>RULES OF CONSTRUCTION</heading>
<section identifier="/us/usc/t1/s2"><num value="2">§ 2.</num><heading> "County" as including "parish", and so forth</heading><content>
<p>The word "county" includes a parish, or any other equivalent subdivision of a State or Territory of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit>(July 30, 1947, ch. 388, 61 Stat. 633.)</sourceCredit>
